    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231840/extras/aeae66514dcee1a383ec4e46346cf5b3.avif?t=1768789754\" width=616 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hydra Coil is a Relaxed Turn-based Space Fantasy RPG</strong> where you explore a miniature cosmos by spaceship, assemble a crew of Voyagers, and uncover the deeper mysteries of the Void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine <i>Heroes of Might and Magic</i>... set in space!<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231840/extras/7c64b2b02bf732d53606858a4488830c.avif?t=1768789754\" width=616 height=98 /></span></p><strong>FEATURES</strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Miniature Cosmos Exploration – </strong>Travel between stars &amp; worlds by spacecraft</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turn-Based Combat – </strong>Battle in space and within exotic atmospheres</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crew –</strong> Recruit Fantastical Creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cosmic Mystery – </strong>Uncover the enigma of the Hydra and the void that surrounds it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Worldbuilding – </strong>Lush visuals and spellbinding ambient soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Editor –</strong> In-game editor for creating and sharing quests</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game does not have:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable Characters (Spaceships only)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grand Strategy, this is not an RTS or 4x style game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Microtransactions</p></li></ul></p>",
